{
    "name": "Kravyad",
    "type": "monster",
    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Description",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "The result of strange magics that rose in the aftermath of the rise of the Eye of Abendego, the always ravenous kravyads constantly travel in search of new prey. They are drawn to shipwrecks, flooded battlefields, and regions experiencing calamitous thunderstorms. A particularly starving kravyad will resort to eating nearly anything, and as such, a kravyad\u2019s \u201ctreasure\u201d typically consists of swallowed items that it failed to digest.<br/><br/> Though intelligent and capable of brutish speech in Aquan, a kravyad is driven mainly by its excessive gluttony. Those seeking to coerce a kravyad into service must rely on either mental enslavement or shows of strength\u2014combined with a steady supply of electrocuted corpses."
        }
    ],
    "html": "<i>Glowing motes of electricity dance over this massive ursine creature\u2019s hairless hide.</i>",
